Hindi pwede.

283
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:42,820
Nagkagulo ang korte.

284
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:44,390
Kailangan natin ang kanyang intel

285
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:45,540
mula sa Yuzao Pleasure House.

286
00:19:46,630 --> 00:19:48,070
Oh, may sasabihin ako sa iyo.

287
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,540
Ang kaso ng katiwalian ay umikot.

288
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:54,710
Sun Changde ng Imperial Stud

289
00:19:54,910 --> 00:19:55,750
